      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment not required at MRL 2. Qualitative equivalency between validation experiment input parameters and COU operating conditions addressed within the Relevance of Validation Activities factor. Key input parameters (flow rate range, rotational speed, fluid viscosity) confirmed comparable between validation and COU contexts as documented in the relevance assessment rationale."
    }
  ],
